</p><div class="cp-assistants hidden"><div><span class="cp-title-label">Contributors:</span><p>&nbsp;</p></div><div><span>0.75 - </span><p><a href="/article/User:Valentino_Braitenberg" title="User:Valentino Braitenberg">Valentino Braitenberg</a>
